#X text 52 63 The filter cuttof input in Pd objects are in hertz \, but the cutoff frequency sweep/modulation is usually done exponentially (as with oscillatos) \, which means we should have a proper input in MIDI pitches and convert to frequency. Below we can compare both ways and try to note the difference \, which can be quite subtle to hear \, but it's easy to understand why it exists. We also have a basic synth structure with an envelope and we retrigger and sync the LFO at everey Note-On., f 78;
